  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To detect a statistically significant increase in the area under the ROC curve when comparing 2-D plus 3-D images to the 2-D images. The ROC curves will be generated from the probability of malignancy scale, a score of 0% to 100%.</measure>
    <time_frame>Fall 2010</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
